    <text>
        <body>
            
            
            <div xml:id="Short13"> 
                <interpGrp type="poembox">
                    <interp ana="#form" type="free"></interp>
                    <interp ana="#tone" type="sad"></interp>
                    <interp ana="#topic" type="death"></interp>
                </interpGrp>
                <lg> 
                    <l>From my mother's sleep I fell into the State,</l>
                    <l>And I hunched in its belly till my wet fur froze.</l>
                    <l>Six miles from earth, loosed from its dream of life,</l>
                    <l>I woke to black flak and the nightmare fighters.</l>
                    <l>When I died they washed me out of the turret with a hose.</l>
                    
